      },
      "findings": [
        "Y1=Y2 identical: beta_fast=16,32 produce same boundaries when L_train=128 (low=0 for both)",
        "All YaRN configs catastrophically bad (PPL@128 329-345 vs Geometric 184.9)",
        "Y4 NTK-aware preserves PPL@128 (189 vs 185) but PPL@8K still much worse than EVQ"
